node.text: Next level trip with the boys to Monterey Car Week.  Next up is Alaska and onward to the top of the Americas.  Followed by Gotham City with Batman in September.  October features Gemballa day in Manhattan and early November we shut down Vegas for the sequel. 🤘🤘📸: @theluketerry
